REQUIREMENTS

Regardless of your operating system, you must have the following things installed on it and included in your path:

  * JRE 1.5 or greater
  * Maven 2.x or greater
  * Git

Under Windows platform you also must have:

  * NSIS 2.x or greater


BUILDING

First of all, open a system shell and check out the sources into some directory. Then cd into the root of the sources and type:

  mvn clean package

The resulting build artifacts will be located under the target directory. That's it.
